#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.88"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.88:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.88:0.2"
msgid "9. Sītivagga"
msgstr "9. Coolness"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.88:0.3"
msgid "88. Sussūsatisutta"
msgstr "88. Wanting to Listen"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.88:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato suṇantopi saddhammaṃ abhabbo niyāmaṃ "
"okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, someone with six qualities is unable to enter the sure path "
"with regards to skillful qualities even when listening to the true teaching."

msgctxt "an6.88:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi chahi?"
msgstr "What six?"

#. VAR: upaṭṭhāpeti → upaṭṭhapeti (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an6.88:1.3"
msgid ""
"Tathāgatappavedite dhammavinaye desiyamāne na sussūsati, na sotaṃ odahati, "
"na aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhāpeti, anatthaṃ gaṇhāti, atthaṃ riñcati, ananulomikāya "
"khantiyā samannāgato hoti."
msgstr ""
"When the teaching and practice proclaimed by the Realized One is being "
"taught they don’t want to listen. They don’t lend an ear or apply their mind "
"to understand them. They learn the incorrect meaning and reject the correct "
"meaning. They accept views that contradict the teaching."

msgctxt "an6.88:1.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato suṇantopi saddhammaṃ "
"abhabbo niyāmaṃ okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Someone with these six qualities is unable to enter the sure path with "
"regards to skillful qualities, even when listening to the true teaching."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.88:2.1"
msgid ""
"Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato suṇanto saddhammaṃ bhabbo niyāmaṃ "
"okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Someone with six qualities is able to enter the sure path with regards to "
"skillful qualities when listening to the true teaching."

msgctxt "an6.88:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi chahi?"
msgstr "What six?"

msgctxt "an6.88:2.3"
msgid ""
"Tathāgatappavedite dhammavinaye desiyamāne sussūsati, sotaṃ odahati, aññā "
"cittaṃ upaṭṭhāpeti, atthaṃ gaṇhāti, anatthaṃ riñcati, anulomikāya khantiyā "
"samannāgato hoti."
msgstr ""
"When the teaching and practice proclaimed by the Realized One is being "
"taught they want to listen. They lend an ear and apply their mind to "
"understand them. They learn the correct meaning and reject the incorrect "
"meaning. They accept views that agree with the teaching."

msgctxt "an6.88:2.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato suṇanto saddhammaṃ bhabbo "
"niyāmaṃ okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattan”ti."
msgstr ""
"Someone with these six qualities is able to enter the sure path with regards "
"to skillful qualities when listening to the true teaching.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.88:2.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
